  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/apple-acknowledges-imessage-issues-on-ios-7-software-update-is/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/apple-imessage-619.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n之前有部分 iOS 7 用户在收发 iMessage 消息时出现了问题（不是<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2012/10/30/apple-imessage-sees-second-outage-in-a-week-itunes-uk-follows/\">第一次</a>发生这种情况了），如今苹果终于给出了回应。在<a href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2013/10/01/imessages-to-nowhere/\">华尔街日报</a>收到的声明中，苹果称只有「不到百分之一」的 iMessage 用户受到了影响，并表示他们会在未来的软件更新中修复这一问题。而 <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/01/apple-says-fraction-of-imessage-users-seeing-issues-working-on-a-fix/\">TechCrunch</a> 则在一份支持资料中找到了一个暂时性的解决办法（想了解的点<a href=\"http://support.apple.com/kb/TS4268\">这里</a>），但如果你懒得去弄的话，只有先靠其它 IM 应用顶一顶啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/02/apple-acknowledges-imessage-issues-on-ios-7-software-update-is/\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2013/10/01/imessages-to-nowhere/\" target=\"_blank\">Wall Street Journal</a><br />\n更多信息：<a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2013/10/01/apple-says-fraction-of-imessage-users-seeing-issues-working-on-a-fix/\" target=\"_blank\">TechCrunch</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/apple-acknowledges-imessage-issues-on-ios-7-software-update-is/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20735444/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/02/apple-acknowledges-imessage-issues-on-ios-7-software-update-is/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><